stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Created
    Created --> Preparing: run_started
    Preparing --> Retrieving: intent_classified / retrieval_plan_built
    Retrieving --> Planning: memory_fused
    Planning --> Executing: plan_generated
    Executing --> Reflecting: steps finished
    Executing --> Failed: run_failed
    Reflecting --> Persisting: run_completed
    Persisting --> Replayable: vector_upserted / profile_updated
    Failed --> Replayable: failure events captured
    Replayable --> [*]
